      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software verification plan with traceability to requirements; regression test suite with >90% coverage of solver modules used in hemolysis computation.",
      "rationale": "SQA documentation covers standard CFD solver modules but lacks traceability for the custom power-law hemolysis post-processor. Regression suite covers 78% of relevant modules. Gap remains at MRL 5."
