      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic pump geometry which is morphologically similar but not identical to the proprietary VAD geometry. Operating point coverage is 5 of 5 required points but geometric similarity index is 0.74, below the 0.90 threshold for direct applicability."
    },
